		<title>06FARMING 2</title>
		<content> A survey of five farms revealed the   
 following;                            
                                       
 a) crops    wheat      100% of farms  
             barley      80% of farms  
             grass (hay) 80% of farms  
             rape        60% of farms  
             potatoes    60% of farms  
             oats        20% of farms  
                                       
 Problems associated with growing these
 crops are the land is heavy,          
 particularly after a rainy spell and  
 this causes drainage problems.        
                                       
 b) livestock  cattle                  
                                       
               beef only 1 farm        
          beef and dairy 1 farm        
          beef and sheep 2 farms       
                 poultry 2 farms       
              no animals 1 farm        </content>
